  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "Just intonation locked. Drama at 0.9 forces partials into near-perfect integer frequency ratios. Play a fifth and hear the 3:2 ratio ring with zero beating. Play a major third and hear 5:4 lock in place. This is what harmony sounded like before equal temperament \u2014 pure, resonant, ancient.",
